{"tid":1592983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十一前！","createTime":"2019-09-25T00:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:22.000Z","uid":326153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45dfcb956e1271b51b96ea92a00280ef80761781","tid":1592983,"uid":326153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:55:32.000Z","msg":"P牌妹，未必有人聽，但你知唔知攪個連登account 幾撚難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪忘記咗十一全球登報賀70事件？一定要留人頭到十一！唯一令我擔心嘅係淋病嗰個假嘅對話會真係有人去，一方面送頭，另一方面就益咗中共做新聞，話好多人好恨同淋病對話，但因為只有百幾個位，坐位不足！<br />\n<br />\n可能會覺得我廢話，但你唸下最近啲風全部都係話示威人數減少，你以為同我哋講呀，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">係對內地講咋！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8d986e41a5bf0a152cb88119b6626bc941cda7a6","tid":1592983,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"6dd2b90f3aba46f507ed5ea85737642caefc9041","tid":1592983,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVsURWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVsURWT.jpg&h=296ee8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsNJLgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsNJLgU.jpg&h=753b112a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUbZiBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUbZiBU.jpg&h=057a85cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8CbVBoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h